      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm just worried because it's a pretty intense pain, almost like a stabbing feeling. but i've had cramps like this before so i guess it's fine. do you think i should take the oxy with something else to make it work better, like a bit of alcohol or maybe some tylenol to ensure i can actually fall asleep? i just really don't want to deal with this tomorrow if i can just knock it out tonight.",
